          "type": "copy",
          "settings": {
            "copy": "<ol><li>Income: increasing net incomes<br/>and security for two million smallholder cotton farmers and workers.</li><li>Empowering women: With a focus on educational training and resources.</li><li>Soil health: Supporting cotton farmers to improve the health of their soil.</li><li>Reducing pesticides: Limiting the use and risk of synthetic pesticides applied by BCI farmers by at least half. </li><li>Greenhouse emissions: Reducing greenhouse gases by 50% per tonne of Better Cotton lint.</li></ol>"
