            "title": "Social working conditions",
            "content_title": "",
            "text": "<p>Manufactured in socially responsible environments where employees have fair working conditions (like reasonable hours and living wages) and there are bans on forced and child labour. It also specifies that occupational health and safety is in place) there is adequate fire protection, building safety, and protective equipment, and that dust, noise, and heat do not threaten workers' health.</p>"
